  m_Name: Getting Started
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  blocks:
  - type: 1
    text: Decontainment is an autonomous bot fighting game. You program and configure
      teams of bots and have them face off against one another in matches. The last
      team standing wins. Get a feel for the bot building process by following these
      instructions.
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 4
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 0
    text: Make a test program
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 3
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 1
    text: "1. Open the program editor and press the \u201CNew\u201D button to make
      a new program.\r\n2. Rename it by right clicking on its name in the list.\r\n3.
      Select it from the list.\r\n4. Drag a TRN instruction block from the code bench
      to the TOP of the code view.\r\n5. Give the degrees field a value of 90.\r"
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 4
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 0
    text: Make a test bot
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 3
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 1
    text: "1. Open the bot editor and press the \u201CNew\u201D button to make a new
      bot.\r\n2. Rename it if you\u2019d like.\r\n3. Select it from the list.\r\n4.
      Give it the test program you made.\r"
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 4
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 0
    text: Make a test team
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 3
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 1
    text: "1. Open the team editor and press the \u201CNew\u201D button to make a
      new team.\r\n2. Rename it if you\u2019d like.\r\n3. Select it from the list.\r\n4.
      Set each member to your test bot.\r"
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 4
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 0
    text: Test your team
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 3
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 1
    text: "1. Open the custom match menu.\r\n2. Select your team for both team 1 and
      team 2.\r\n3. Select the \u201Csys_null\u201D map.\r\n4. Start the match.\r"
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 4
    text: 
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - type: 1
    text: "All bots should spin clockwise until the match ends. You can press the
      abort button to stop the match early.\r\n\r\nThis is the general flow of Decontainment.
      Build teams of bots and test them against other teams. See if you can build
      a team that can beat the built-in bots.\r\n"
    image: {fileID: 0}
    imageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
